{"tid":2216634,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[正邪對決] 沙巴議會選舉（9月26日）討論區","createTime":"2020-09-25T00:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T18:37:01.000Z","uid":53673,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1183b12195bdf4d70751efc3b142c624b7646693","tid":2216634,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T00:26:45.000Z","msg":"正義陣營：民興黨+希望聯盟<br />\n邪惡陣營：國民聯盟<br />\n<br />\n今次選舉起因：<br />\n因為不斷有政棍議員（aka 青蛙）跳槽去國盟<br />\n跳到本來執政既民興黨+希盟議席少過半數<br />\n對家國盟欲發動政變奪權<br />\n但比沙巴首長沙菲益阿達搶先一步解散議會重選<br />\n<br />\n選舉意義：<br />\n今次選舉係自大馬3月「喜來登政變」、希盟倒台後第一場選舉<br />\n將會揭示民意對慕尤丁既國盟新政權、跳槽政治是否支持<br />\n更會影響國會是否解散重選、希盟+能否翻盤、安華/沙菲益能否出任首相等重大議題<br />\n<br />\n沙巴昨日新增武肺感染：<br />\n69人<br />\n（但照選到，摑柒婆一巴）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更多資訊：<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/2020年沙巴州選舉\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F2020%E5%B9%B4%E6%B2%99%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%9E%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=1ff0e895\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/2020年沙巴州選舉</a>"},{"pid":"98e1a489a0f504279ebc0b7bb004d0fbd41b1565","tid":2216634,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T00:30:40.000Z","msg":"安華好似尋日話獲得大多數支持，可以做首相喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f65802f2149c13b6943dbebb657ffab101da75","tid":2216634,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T00:32:01.000Z","msg":"沙巴人口比例被清洗到咁，想唔輸都難"},{"pid":"caaa1a186917a993c081827f3d85abfa97f85d4b","tid":2216634,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98e1a489a0f504279ebc0b7bb004d0fbd41b1565","tid":2216634,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T00:30:40.000Z","msg":"安華好似尋日話獲得大多數支持，可以做首相喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c